CDISCPILOT01,103,01,AE,5,EX,3,AETRIG
CDISCPILOT01,103,01,AE,6,EX,3,AETRIG
CDISCPILOT01,104,01,AE,1,EX,1,AETRIG
CDISCPILOT01,104,01,AE,2,EX,1,AETRIG
CDISCPILOT01,104,01,AE,3,EX,2,AETRIG
CDISCPILOT01,104,01,AE,4,EX,2,AETRIG
